Farafina kɛŋna [[Purkina Fasoo|Purkinaa Fasoo]] ɛjaɖɛ taa hendu teyaa kɩgaʊ ŋgbɛyɛ naɖɩyɛ nɛ ɖɩñɔ peeɖe kɛ pɩnaɣ [[1978]]. Farafina weyi payaɣ-ɩ se Mahama Konaté yɔ, ɛmakɩ ɖoŋaɣ kamaɣ fɛyɩ. Ɛ-wayɩ lɛ Souleymane Sanou wɛŋna nɛ ɛcɔŋna pɛ-ŋgbɛyɛ nɖɩ ɖɩ-yɔɔ. Souleymane Sanou ɛnɛ, ɛñaɣ pana nɛ ɛcɔɔ ajɛya sakɩyɛ nɛ ɛla maamaacinaa nɛ pɩkɛdɩna ɛyaa. 

[[File:الرقص الأفريقي 123.jpg|thumb|الرقص الأفريقي 123]]
Hendu teyaa ŋgbɛyɛ nɖɩ payaɣ ɖɩɖɩ se Rolling Stones yɔ, ɖɩɩya-yɛ nɛ patɩŋga pɛkpɛndɩ nɛ palɩzɩ hendu teu kɩlɛmɩŋ kanahaʊ nakʊyʊ nɛ payaɣ-kʊ se Continental Drift, pʊtɔbʊʊ se: ɛjaɖɛ tɛma. Pʊwayɩ lɛ, Jon Hassell  tasɩɩ yaʊ nɛ ɛna-ɩ palɩzɩ kɩlɛmɩŋ kanahaʊ ŋgʊ payaɣ-kʊ  se ''Flash of the Spirit'' kɛ pɩnaɣ 1987. 

[[File:الرقص الأفريقي 987.jpg|thumb|الرقص الأفريقي 987]]
Pɩnaɣ 1988 taa kɛ Farafina cala labʊ amʊʊzɛ kɛ Wɛmbley tɛtʊ taa nɛ ɛɖʊ [[Nelson Mandela]] hɩɖɛ. Ɖooo ɛzɩ palɩzɩɣ Farafina  kɩgaʊ ŋgbɛyɛ ɖɩnɛ kɛ pɩnzɩ 1980 waa taa yɔ, mba pawɛ pɩtaa yɔ  pa-taa kɔyɔ: Souleymane Sanou, Chekere, Soungalo Coulibaly. Sɔnɔ mbʊ yɔ, pɩnaɣ 2012 taa 2012 taa ɛyaa mba pɔsɔza pɔ-yɔɔ yɔ paba yɔ: Fatoumata Dembele, Moussa Sanou, Seydou Dembele, Salif Ouattara, Lamoussa Sanou, Boakary Dembele.
